section.t:
The input is an associative array. For example: array( 'module' => 'articles', 'variable' => 'pubtype1');
or: array( 'module' => 'articles', 'object' => 'pubtype1', 'action' => 'display');
So there would be a table for 2*n number of inputs. (the key is one string to be looked for, and the values are other) All which will be assigned id numbers.
And then select on a specialized table for the given number of inputs the unique ID looked for.
